Upcoming Records Staff Tips (http://UpcomingRecords.com)

If you would like to become staff in our room just follow these (very easy) steps.

1) Do not ask to be staff.
2) Recruit other active members to our community.
3) Be active and nice to other members of the community.
4) Do not meh every songs or make negative comments; We believe in positive reinforcement.
5) Respect the rules and take them seriously. (http://tinyurl.com/upcomingrecords-rules)

Resident DJ: Play a lot of good music.
Bouncer: Correctly identify when people break rules and ping staff when things go wrong in the room.
